---
title: Prawns, Wontons & Asian Veggie Stir-Fry with Garlic Rice & Sweet Chilli Sriracha Sauce
description: We love a wonton - delicate little bundles of savoury goodness that are a joy to eat! Let’s serve them up with fluffy rice and Asian veggies stir-fried with ginger, garlic and soy. Drizzle over a sweet and spicy sauce for extra flavour!

